      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really dont want to go back to the clinic, it costs way too much and they're closed now anyway. i feel okay otherwise, just don't have a fever or anything. is it really that serious? could i just use some neosporin and a bandage for a day or two and see if it settles down?",
