      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay good to know. i a bit worried about the yellow stuff tho, it's looking a bit thick and it smells slightly sweet? is it possible it's just normal serous fluid or something? if i just keep the neosporin on it and maybe take some ibuprofen for the warmth/pain, it should be fine right? i'll just wait until monday to see if it gets better.",
