      "content": "That sweet smell and thick discharge are usually signs that your body is fighting something, not just normal fluid. Since you're worried, you need to be proactive. While ibuprofen will manage the pain, you should definitely try to get a proper diagnosis now, not wait until Monday. For a serious infection, you need a prescription-strength treatment, and I highly recommend you try to get an appointment today, or use a local pharmacy for an immediate, targeted treatment.",
